  "texts": [
    "The offline version is not directly exposed to the GPT-4 LM online database but uses some of its intelligence trained on the customized factory data to respond to users' queries.",
    "We designed the online version through the new GPT-4 feature, which allows users to configure and create customized GPTs based on their requirements.The advantage of the offline version is a more secure working environment because the factory data is not available online on the web or through OpenAI.",
    "The disadvantage is limited exposure to the extensive GPT-4 LM database, which can suggest several more recommendations and more detailed responses to each query received.",
    "The advantages and disadvantages of the online version are the opposite of the offline version.",
    "The advantage is the richer responses and recommendations thanks to the online GPT-4 LM database, and the disadvantage is the security risk of loading the factory data online to the web and OpenAI.The factory's customized application has a security layer."
  ],
